---
import Header from './Header.astro';
import Footer from './Footer.astro';
import Sidebar from './Sidebar.astro';
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '@/components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />
  <column align-="center" self-="grow" id="container">
    <column id="center">
      <Header />

      <row self-="grow" id="content" gap-="1">
        <Sidebar />
        <column id="preview" self-="grow !basis">
          <column gap-="1" data-id="flow">
            <column>
              <span>flow</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>Created in collaboration with Raycast, Flow is a medium roast from the Sidama region of Ethiopia. Featuring notes segfault of red berries, tropical fruits, and caramel, this is the best way to get in the flow â€” the perfect state of productivity.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="cron">
            <column>
              <span>cron</span>
              <p>12oz</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$30</strong>
            <p>Subscribe to Cron, the official Terminal membership and. Each month you'll receive a scheduled delivery with a special flavor-of-the-month blend. You'll also get receive additional gifts, exclusive offers, and invites to Terminal events.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="artisan">
            <column>
              <span>artisan</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>Working the backend and frontend of the palette, this new artisinal infusion is a collaboration with Laravel from Colombia and Papua New Guinea and is full stack in flavour and texture.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="object-object">
            <column>
              <span>[object Object]</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>The interpolation of Caturra and Castillo varietals from Las Cochitas creates this refreshing citrusy and complex coffee.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="segfault">
            <column>
              <span>segfault</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>A savory yet sweet blend created from a natural fault in the coffee cherry that causes it to develop one bean instead of two.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="dark-mode">
            <column>
              <span>dark mode</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>A dark roast from the Cerrado region of Brazil, an expansive lush and tropical savanna that creates a dark chocolate blend with hints of almond.</p>
          </column>

          <column gap-="1" data-id="404">
            <column>
              <span>404</span>
              <p>medium roast | 12oz | whole beans</p>
            </column>
            <strong>$22</strong>
            <p>A flavorful decaf coffee processed in the mountain waters of Brazil to create a dark chocolatey blend.</p>
          </column>
        </column>
      </row>

      <Footer />
    </column>
  </column>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
#preview {
  [data-id] {
    display: none;
  }
}

#content:has(button[variant-="flow"]:focus), 
#content:not(:has(button:focus)) {
  [data-id="flow"] {
    display: flex;
  }
}

#content:has(button[variant-="cron"]:focus) [data-id="cron"] { display: flex; }
#content:has(button[variant-="artisan"]:focus) [data-id="artisan"] { display: flex; }
#content:has(button[variant-="object-object"]:focus) [data-id="object-object"] { display: flex; }
#content:has(button[variant-="segfault"]:focus) [data-id="segfault"] { display: flex; }
#content:has(button[variant-="dark-mode"]:focus) [data-id="dark-mode"] { display: flex; }
#content:has(button[variant-="404"]:focus) [data-id="404"] { display: flex; }

</style>

<style is:global>
  #center {
    max-width: 58ch;
    max-height: 28lh;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1lh;
    padding: 0 1ch;
  }

  .secondary {
    color: var(--foreground2);
  }

  #footer [is-="separator"] {
    width: 100%;
    --separator-color: var(--foreground2);
  }

  #content {
    width: 100%;
  }

  #sidebar {
    min-width: 20ch;
  }

  #header {
    row {
      padding: 1lh 2ch;
      flex-grow: 1;
      flex-basis: 0;
      align-items: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    div[is-="separator"] {
      height: calc(2lh - 2px);
    }
  }
</style>
